{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "马蒂 第3话 老爸的遗产",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "嘿咻……该出发了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯？马蒂，你要去哪里？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这么大包的行李……\\n难道是要出城？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "嗯？是要出城一趟，\\n不过我去去就回。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "啊，这样吗。\\n看你背着这么大包的行李，\\n我还以为你又要去遗迹里探险呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那你是要去哪里？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "我要去把这些宝物\\n摆放到我的博物馆里。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦！？\\n马蒂你拥有博物馆吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "这还用问吗？以博物馆长为目标，\\n又是最强的寻宝猎人，\\n没有摆放宝物的地方说不过去吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "方便的话，\\n你们也一起来看看？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "可以吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "那当然了！\\n博物馆就是为了让人参观的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢谢。\\n那我去叫大家！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "看呐！那栋建筑物\\n就是我的博物馆！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "喔……没想到你还有房产，\\n真厉害啊，马蒂。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "嘿嘿。其实我是从\\n上代馆长的老爸手上继承的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你父亲也是博物馆长啊。\\n真是了不起的父亲。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "是啊。\\n我很尊敬老爸。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以，你才想成为\\n像你的父亲那样的人吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "不……我并不想\\n成为像老爸那样的博物馆长。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "咦，为什么？\\n你不是说很尊敬他吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "是啊，我很尊敬他。\\n老爸他很伟大。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "用自己获得的宝物，为大家带来笑容。\\n也让我喜欢上了宝物！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "那么，你刚才说不想成为\\n像你父亲那样的人，是为什么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "因为老爸在最后关头\\n夺走了大家的笑容。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "最后关头？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "他死了。他去搜集用于展出的宝物……\\n结果一去不回。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "大家说看见宝物会睹物思人，\\n觉得很悲伤，于是渐渐地，\\n大家都不来博物馆了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "他希望大家看见宝物后能露出笑容，\\n但让大家伤心不就本末倒置了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "所以，我不想变成老爸那样的人。\\n我必须成为最强。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "喂喂，别一脸伤感啊。\\n来，去看看宝物，开心一下吧。\\n我们走！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "原来是这样。\\n所以马蒂才那么执着于最强……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。\\n马蒂也很努力呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}